\begin_inset Formula $x_{t-1}^{(i)},\: x_{t}$
\end_inset

 is substituted by 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{t}^{(i)}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}$
\end_inset

